original_title: Comedy Workshop: Love and Maud Carver
overview: Maud has two men in her life - George and Errol. In an effort to decide which boyfriend to keep, she visits a clairvoyant who tells her that her ideal partner may, in fact, be a third person she has yet to meet. Recorded in a single studio, with minimalist sets. - From IMDB
title: Comedy Workshop: Love and Maud Carver
